[normal]Transforming the existing practitioner registration pilot schemes around the UK into a UK-wide scheme, with a target of a 2014 launch;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Investigation of the policy and practice issues which will need to be addressed in order to introduce successfully a Skills Passport for individual members of the public health workforce;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Discussions about implementation of revalidation for public health specialists (not covered by the General Medical Council’s revalidation scheme);
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Participation in the activities of the Public Health Workforce Advisory Group.
